What is a Module?
A python file with functions, classes and other components 

Why use Modules?
Break code down into reusable structures

Example: 
from random import randint --- specific import the randint function and nothing else

A module is something we have created in other file 

What is a Package?
It is a published collections fo modules

[python package index] https://pypi.org/
    
install from a list of packages --- pip install -r requirements.txt

Virtual Environment 
pip install virtualenv # install the Virtual Environment 

virtualenv <folder name> 